memberdef.name: RETRIEVE
memberdef.initializer: do { \ if (evtStore()->contains<TYPE>(NAME)) \ ATH_CHECK( evtStore()->retrieve( CONTAINER, NAME ) ); \ else \ Warning("calcDiTauVariables","%s container is not available", NAME); \ } while(false) \

briefdescription.para: Helper macros for checking and retrieving xAOD containers.
